I"³<h1 id="overview">Overview</h1>

<p>Use <a href="/v0.34/networks/docker-compose/">Docker Compose</a> to spin up Tendermint testnets on your
local machine.</p>

<p>Use <a href="/v0.34/networks/terraform-and-ansible/">Terraform and Ansible</a> to deploy Tendermint
testnets to the cloud.</p>

<p>See the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tendermint testnet --help</code> command for more help initializing testnets.</p>
